OysterMate
==========

OysterMate is an Android application for viewing your OysterCard balance, auto
top-up value and season ticket information.

It also features buttons to send you to the TfL OysterCard web site for
adding credit or season tickets/travelcards to your OysterCard.

New features to be included are:
 * Viewing your journey history
 * Map for locations of Oyster top-up locations

